!! Code

Inline `code` and a fenced code block with a language tag:

```javascript
function add(a, b) {
	return a + b; // highlighted as JS
}
```

Fenced block without a language tag:

```
plain preformatted text
no language highlighting
```

Typed blocks render their content as the given type:

$$$text/css
.foo { color: red; }
$$$

$$$text/vnd.tiddlywiki
This is ''wikitext'' inside a typed block.
$$$

